{"tid":718243,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［急問］皮膚敏感定點","createTime":"2018-06-26T15:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T02:17:02.000Z","uid":159282,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"657d172361df7abd83df36782b67f3d27a9f8fb5","tid":718243,"uid":159282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:40:51.000Z","msg":"上星期感冒完之後 <br />\n依幾日成身都出咗啲一粒粒嘅嘢 <br />\n（之前有幾次病完都會咁 通常一個禮拜左右會退曬）<br />\n一開頭覺得係自己免疫系統差 加上公司空氣唔多流通（做緊X澤） 有啲同事都有皮膚敏感<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/234042_b5d315c5d0415b09f8566c962dba11fa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F234042_b5d315c5d0415b09f8566c962dba11fa.png&h=1bbcef16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想問聲大家到底我係皮膚敏感 定係其他皮膚問題<br />\n同埋如果去睇皮膚科嘅話 大家會唔會有啲好推薦<br />\n多謝大家先"},{"pid":"4a949fe8f0f692f1d4ef7c28eca4be4a052549fb","tid":718243,"uid":50779,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:42:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af7f5a49651517e88fcd7dd63f80ab78b262e302","tid":718243,"uid":149844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:43:12.000Z","msg":"睇皮膚科啦<br />\n上連登問作用不大<br />\n同埋巴打你好瘦"},{"pid":"03667b9f48d64a9137810445ee60fadbb5d8e03b","tid":718243,"uid":21306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:43:46.000Z","msg":"瘦到..."},{"pid":"dc2ae0faa55836f776340143242ff2d3a76ed73a","tid":718243,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:46:03.000Z","msg":"巴打咁瘦睇下醫生好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f041277b41a9480c0e0be574f1d035b2f4e1fbb7","tid":718243,"uid":63976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:48:11.000Z","msg":"痕唔痕？<br />\n之前都試過感冒睇中醫食中藥<br />\n食完就成身出咗好多一點點 好似你咁<br />\n個中醫話係排緊身體啲毒出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都係一星期左右就退哂"},{"pid":"6371519dd07997bf360b43bdbbc295d4dd0e90b7","tid":718243,"uid":159282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f041277b41a9480c0e0be574f1d035b2f4e1fbb7","tid":718243,"uid":63976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:48:11.000Z","msg":"痕唔痕？<br />\n之前都試過感冒睇中醫食中藥<br />\n食完就成身出咗好多一點點 好似你咁<br />\n個中醫話係排緊身體啲毒出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都係一星期左右就退哂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:53:40.000Z","msg":"早幾日痕 依幾日冇咁痕<br />\n我諗應該都係病完排毒嫁啦<br />\n過一兩日去搵中藥醫師執翻劑<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">藥</span></span>先得"},{"pid":"59428da3a775966dab0a53a60fd26df1750d5720","tid":718243,"uid":18479,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:53:57.000Z","msg":"分唔到手定腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5510899590559c3ae238c4a1fdaff13e4a13b7f3","tid":718243,"uid":159282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"03667b9f48d64a9137810445ee60fadbb5d8e03b","tid":718243,"uid":21306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:43:46.000Z","msg":"瘦到..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:55:43.000Z","msg":"好瘦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n~179CM 64KG<br />\n已經晚晚食兩碗到飯 有肉有菜<br />\n我仲嫌我肚腩突突地"},{"pid":"7aec3029b2abee08a8a4d97bc1c38554fc8b88fc","tid":718243,"uid":159282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59428da3a775966dab0a53a60fd26df1750d5720","tid":718243,"uid":18479,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:53:57.000Z","msg":"分唔到手定腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:56:06.000Z","msg":"有手掌嘅腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"521084ecbcab6452a6299d3d6882d272d193892d","tid":718243,"uid":18479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7aec3029b2abee08a8a4d97bc1c38554fc8b8